<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
<title>UDMS / Freshsales Integration Overview &mdash; Edusport Travel and Tours</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    background: #f0f4f8;
    color: #1a1a18;
    padding: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* Branded top bar */
  .top-bar {
    background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #1553A0;
    padding: 0 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 64px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(21,83,160,0.08);
  }
  .top-bar img {
    height: 40px;
    display: block;
  }
  .top-bar-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1553A0;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid #AECDE8;
    background: #D6E4F5;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px 24px 32px;
  }

  /* Page header */
  .header {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    border-left: 4px solid #1553A0;
    padding-left: 12px;
  }
  .header h1 {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1553A0;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }
  .header p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #6b6b68;
  }

  /* System name pills */
  .pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 9px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
  .pill-udms  { background: #D6E4F5; color: #1553A0; border: 1px solid #AECDE8; }
  .pill-fresh { background: #D5EFD4; color: #2A8A27; border: 1px solid #A3D4A1; }
  .pill-both  { background: #FFF3D0; color: #7A5A00; border: 1px solid #F0CC6E; }

  /* System summary cards */
  .systems-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .sys-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #dde3eb;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
  }
  .sys-card.udms-card { border-top: 3px solid #1553A0; }
  .sys-card.fresh-card { border-top: 3px solid #3CAF35; }
  .sys-card .sys-name {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .sys-card p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #6b6b68;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Main grid */
  .main-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  /* Flow cards */
  .flow-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #dde3eb;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 14px 8px;
  }
  .flow-card.udms-flow { border-top: 3px solid #1553A0; }
  .flow-card.fresh-flow { border-top: 3px solid #3CAF35; }
  .flow-card.both-flow  { border-top: 3px solid #E0B020; }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #9b9b97;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .direction-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .arrow-blue  { font-size: 15px; color: #1553A0; font-weight: 700; }
  .arrow-green { font-size: 15px; color: #2A8A27; font-weight: 700; }
  .arrow-both  { font-size: 15px; color: #7A5A00; font-weight: 700; }

  /* Flow rows */
  .flow-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 28px 1fr;
    align-items: start;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 7px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0ec;
  }
  .flow-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .num {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .num-blue  { background: #D6E4F5; color: #1553A0; }
  .num-green { background: #D5EFD4; color: #2A8A27; }
  .num-amber { background: #FFF3D0; color: #7A5A00; }

  .flow-text { line-height: 1.4; }
  .flow-text strong {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a18;
    display: block;
  }
  .flow-text span {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #6b6b68;
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  /* Right column stack */
  .right-stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }

  /* Decision resolved card */
  .decision-card {
    background: #EBF7EB;
    border: 1px solid #7DC97A;
    border-top: 3px solid #3CAF35;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px;
  }
  .decision-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1E6E1B;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .resolved-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 6px 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #1a1a18;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .resolved-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: #D5EFD4;
    border: 1px solid #A3D4A1;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    color: #1E6E1B;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .resolved-detail {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #2A6B28;
    margin-top: 2px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer-note {
    margin-top: 14px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    background: #1553A0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media print {
    body { background: #fff; }
    .top-bar { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }
    .footer-note { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }
    .page { padding: 16px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Branded header bar -->
<div class="top-bar">
  <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Edusport Travel and Tours">
  <span class="top-bar-label">Systems Integration</span>
</div>

<div class="page">

  <!-- Page header -->
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Integration overview: what goes where</h1>
    <p>UDMS (booking system) and Freshsales CRM data flow &mdash; 15 integration points, matching logic confirmed</p>
  </div>

  <!-- System summaries -->
  <div class="systems-row">
    <div class="sys-card udms-card">
      <div class="sys-name"><span class="pill pill-udms">UDMS</span></div>
      <p>Internal travel booking system. Handles quotes, bookings, supplier management, finance, and customer documents.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sys-card fresh-card">
      <div class="sys-name"><span class="pill pill-fresh">Freshsales CRM</span></div>
      <p>Customer-facing CRM. Manages all enquiries, the sales pipeline, marketing communications, and source attribution.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main flows grid -->
  <div class="main-grid">

    <!-- UDMS to Freshsales -->
    <div class="flow-card udms-flow">
      <div class="section-label">UDMS tells Freshsales when&hellip;</div>
      <div class="direction-row">
        <span class="pill pill-udms">UDMS</span>
        <span class="arrow-blue">&#8594;</span>
        <span class="pill pill-fresh">Freshsales</span>
      </div>

      <div class="flow-item">
        <div class="num num-blue">1</div>
        <div class="flow-text">
          <strong>A quote status changes</strong>
          <span>Update the Freshsales pipeline stage</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-item">
        <div class="num num-blue">2</div>
        <div class="flow-text">
          <strong>A booking status changes</strong>
          <span>Update the Freshsales pipeline stage</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-item">
        <div class="num num-blue">3</div>
        <div class="flow-text">
          <strong>Agent manually enters the UDMS reference into Freshsales</strong>
          <span>One-time step per enquiry &mdash; this link activates all automated sync (points 1, 2, 4&ndash;7)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-item">
        <div class="num num-blue">4</div>
        <div class="flow-text">
          <strong>A quote or booking value is set</strong>
          <span>Sync the monetary value into Freshsales deal value</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-item">
        <div class="num num-blue">5</div>
        <div class="flow-text">
          <strong>Correspondence is sent or received</strong>
          <span>Copy into the Freshsales enquiry activity log</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-item">
        <div class="num num-blue">6</div>
        <div class="flow-text">
          <strong>Travel dates are set or changed</strong>
          <span>Update departure and return date fields in Freshsales</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-item">
        <div class="num num-blue">7</div>
        <div class="flow-text">
          <strong>A booking form is received and accepted</strong>
          <span>Flag the corresponding Freshsales enquiry accordingly</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right column -->
    <div class="right-stack">

      <!-- Freshsales to UDMS -->
      <div class="flow-card fresh-flow">
        <div class="section-label">Freshsales tells UDMS when&hellip;</div>
        <div class="direction-row">
          <span class="pill pill-fresh">Freshsales</span>
          <span class="arrow-green">&#8594;</span>
          <span class="pill pill-udms">UDMS</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-item">
          <div class="num num-green">8</div>
          <div class="flow-text">
            <strong>An enquiry source is captured</strong>
            <span>Write to UDMS Sales Analysis 4 &mdash; critical for reporting</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-item">
          <div class="num num-green">9</div>
          <div class="flow-text">
            <strong>A customer phone number is captured</strong>
            <span>Push to UDMS &mdash; new field required in UDMS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-item">
          <div class="num num-green">10</div>
          <div class="flow-text">
            <strong>A customer location is captured</strong>
            <span>Push to UDMS &mdash; new field required in UDMS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bidirectional -->
      <div class="flow-card both-flow">
        <div class="section-label">Always kept in sync (both directions)</div>
        <div class="direction-row">
          <span class="pill pill-both">UDMS</span>
          <span class="arrow-both">&#8644;</span>
          <span class="pill pill-both">Freshsales</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-item">
          <div class="num num-amber">11</div>
          <div class="flow-text"><strong>Customer name</strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-item">
          <div class="num num-amber">12</div>
          <div class="flow-text"><strong>Customer email address</strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-item">
          <div class="num num-amber">13</div>
          <div class="flow-text">
            <strong>Sport type</strong>
            <span>Freshsales field &#8644; UDMS Sales Analysis 1</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-item">
          <div class="num num-amber">14</div>
          <div class="flow-text">
            <strong>Sport event interest</strong>
            <span>Freshsales field &#8644; UDMS Sales Analysis 2</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-item">
          <div class="num num-amber">15</div>
          <div class="flow-text"><strong>Agent / travel agent account</strong></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Resolved decision block -->
      <div class="decision-card">
        <div class="decision-title">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6.5" stroke="#1E6E1B" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <polyline points="5,8.5 7,10.5 11,6" stroke="#1E6E1B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
          </svg>
          How the systems connect: confirmed
        </div>
        <div class="resolved-row">
          <span class="resolved-label">Phase 1 &mdash; Manual</span>
          <div>
            <div>When an enquiry arrives, the two systems have <strong>no automatic link</strong>.</div>
            <div class="resolved-detail">Once the agent creates a quote in UDMS, they manually add the UDMS reference number to the corresponding Freshsales enquiry record. This is the one-time linking step per enquiry.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resolved-row" style="margin-top:8px">
          <span class="resolved-label">Phase 2 &mdash; Automated</span>
          <div>
            <div>Once the reference is in Freshsales, <strong>all automated sync begins</strong>.</div>
            <div class="resolved-detail">The 15 integration flows above operate automatically from that point forward &mdash; status changes, values, dates, correspondence, and field sync all run without agent intervention.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-note">
    All 15 integration points are defined. Connection logic is confirmed: agent manually adds the UDMS reference to Freshsales once per enquiry, after which all automated sync operates. No outstanding decisions &mdash; development can begin.
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
